1. Project Title
Smart Blood Bank Management System â€“ Donor & Patient Record Automation
2. Abstract
The Smart Blood Bank Management System is a lightweight web-based application designed to maintain donor information, patient requests, blood stock details, and transaction records.
The application helps hospitals, organizations, and blood banks manage operations efficiently by providing features such as donor listing, patient registration, search and filtering, data import/export, and record maintenance.
The project is hosted on AWS S3 (Static Hosting) and optionally uses AWS EC2 for backend expansion.
3. Objective
â€¢	To digitize blood donor and patient management.
â€¢	To maintain accurate and up-to-date blood availability records.
â€¢	To speed up emergency blood requirement search.
â€¢	To reduce manual paperwork and human errors.
â€¢	To allow exporting/importing of donor & patient data.
